## üìö Resources for Understanding

### For Those New to Open Source:
- [How to Contribute to Open Source](https://opensource.guide/how-to-contribute/)
- [GitHub's Guide to Contributing](https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/quickstart/contributing-to-projects)

### For Understanding Dual-Layer Framework:
- [Project Documentation](docs/complete-documentation.md) - Section 5: Dual-Layer Framework
- Scientific Layer: Proven, testable principles
- Energetic Layer: Keylontic Science interpretation
- Both valid, neither required

### For Conflict Resolution:
- Assume good intentions first
- Ask clarifying questions
- Use "I feel/think" statements
- Seek to understand before being understood
- Involve maintainers if needed

